snippet.title: Kingdom Eighties | Gameplay Teaser And Console Announcement
snippet.description:
Wishlist NOW! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1956040/Kingdom_Eighties/ 

The summer camp is just the beginning! In Kingdom Eighties, you will travel through different locations never seen before in the micro-strategy series. Take a peek at the new settings in this gameplay teaser. 

Kingdom Eighties is coming to PC, Nintendo Switch, Xbox Series S/X and PlayStation 5 in 2023.
